title: Little Tikes Lil’ Ocean Explorers Crawl ‘n Pop Turtle

asset.author: Little Tikes
asset.description:
Get ready for a sea of smiles with the Little Tikes Lil’ Ocean Explorers Crawl ‘N Pop Turtle. It’s a shape sorter that crawls, encouraging baby to chase after it. The shapes pop out, encouraging baby to sort them and start the chasing fun all over again.

transcripts: Get ready for a sea of smiles with the little tikes little ocean explorers crawling pop turtle. A shape order with a twist designed for babies from six to thirty six months. Little tikes crawling pop turtle help people learn about shapes and colors while encouraging crawling at the same time. Younger babies can use crawl and pop turtle is a classic shapes sorter by placing colorful blocks into the turtle shell. When baby is ready to crawl the turtle zigzag movements encourage them to chase and crawl across the floor after it. Baby just press on the turtle head to make it crawl and play lively music. Once it stops the shapes fall out encouraging baby sorting them and start chasing fun all over again. The little tikes little ocean explorers crawl and popped her doll teach baby moving and help develop fine motor skills and eye coordination problem solving and more.
